</emphasis>
, female, 
<collectingCountry box="[1111,1218,888,910]" name="Bolivia" pageId="12" pageNumber="517">BOLIVIA</collectingCountry>
, Rio Songo, with two labels: “ 
<collectingCountry box="[289,367,918,940]" name="Bolivia" pageId="12" pageNumber="517">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
, Rio Songo, 
<quantity box="[521,581,918,940]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="517" unit="m" value="800.0">800m</quantity>
, Fassl” and handwritten label “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Zerny" authorityName="Zerny" box="[935,1249,918,940]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Pompiliodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="517" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="acroleuca">Pompiliodes acroleuca Zerny</taxonomicName>
♀ 
<typeStatus box="[1296,1344,918,940]" pageId="12" pageNumber="517">type</typeStatus>
